title: Djembe Drum Jam
description:
Djembe Drum Jam is a virtual version of the diabolic ethnic musical instrument Djembe Drum. You can use it anywhere in the street jams or enjoying headphones, Djembe will always be with you and give instant sound meditation. Enjoy the freedom of sound, no longer need to carry 5 pounds with an tree in your android smartphone all that may be necessary to activate the application and play in the mountains, the sea, around the campfire or in the countryside. Go to jam with guitar sounds and other drums, as well as the sounds of synthesizers. With Djembe Drum Jam you get a sound artist, weave their own rhythms, create! 

-= Features =-
- Multi Touch supported!!!
- Really Djembe Drum Sounds. 
- Best ethnic musical instrument Djembe Drum always with you.
- High quality sound samples.
- Enjoy the music .
- Use in street music jams.
- Maximum volume.
- Implemented a dynamic volume, now sound more lively.
- Added multisampling.
